nanu śaivādīnāṃ kim etad asti | ata āha—ratnapuram ityādi | ratnaṃ maṇiḥ | tad eva puraṃ sthānaṃ yasya sukharūpābhimatasya tad ratnapuram | kiñjalke patitam | jalatāṃ niḥsāratām | rudro bhagavān | yugme samāpattau | śivaḥ kalyāṇāvāhakaḥ | ata eva śreṣṭhaḥ | saiva tattvaṃ śaktiś cidrūpā | parāc chreṣṭhāt parā śreṣṭhā tad eva ||
